CLIENT’S  FEEDBACK
</div> </div> </div> <div class="lg:pl-16 pl-8 lg:pb-12 bg-[#141414] pb-20" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="flex flex-row flex-1 overflow-hidden" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="post pr-12" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="clients-title mt-16 mb-8" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> Transform workplace safety with SafeConnect </div> <div class="clients-description" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> A behavior-based safety (BBS) app designed to foster a proactive safety culture. By focusing on observing and improving behaviors, this app helps organizations reduce risks, enhance compliance, and promote a safer work environment. With secure data handling and real-time insights, SafeConnect is the ultimate tool for creating lasting safety habits. </div> <div class="client-name mt-8" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> Sathish </div> <div class="client-position" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> Project Manager </div> </div><div class="post pr-12" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="clients-title mt-16 mb-8" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> Gratitude to SPI for Exceptional EMS Software Development and Support </div> <div class="clients-description" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> I want to thank Software Professionals, Inc. (SPI) for the development and implementation of Environmental Maintenance System (EMS) software application. SPI continues to provide exceptional support for upgrades and application hosting on the cloud. EMS inspection and maintenance reporting application continues to exceed our expectations. The key factors for choosing to work with SPI was their flexibility, in-depth technical knowledge, dedication and innovative software application solutions. </div> <div class="client-name mt-8" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> Jen </div> <div class="client-position" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> Environmental Manager </div> </div><div class="post pr-12" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="clients-title mt-16 mb-8" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> The Difference SafeConnect Made for Us! </div> <div class="clients-description" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> SafeConnect has revolutionized our workplace safety culture. The app actively engages our employees in identifying risks and sharing best practices, leading to a noticeable decrease in incidents. Its focus on observation and intervention has made safety a habit for our team, creating a hazard-free environment that we can all feel proud of! </div> <div class="client-name mt-8" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> Jeffry Jones </div> <div class="client-position" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> CEO, Neo Technologies </div> </div><div class="post pr-12" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="clients-title mt-16 mb-8" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> Safe and Secure Product </div> <div class="clients-description" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> SafeConnect has revolutionized our workplace safety culture. The app actively engages our employees in identifying risks and sharing best practices, leading to a noticeable decrease in incidents. Its focus on observation and intervention has made safety a habit for our team, creating a hazard-free environment that we can all feel proud of! </div> <div class="client-name mt-8" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> Karthik </div> <div class="client-position" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> CEO, Kytz Labs </div> </div><div class="post pr-12" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> <div class="clients-title mt-16 mb-8" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> Safe and Secure Product </div> <div class="clients-description" data-astro-cid-j7pv25f6> EnviroConnect has immensely helped our environmental management by streamlining regulatory compliance, reducing paper usage, and providing instant access to digital records during inspections. The app&#39;s real-time data tracking and reporting capabilities have proven invaluable during surprise inspections, allowing users to quickly generate comprehensive reports that showcase compliance history and proactive measures. With cloud-based storage ensuring secure and easily retrievable environmental records, EnviroConne